      *              * Emissione tag 'IdCodice'                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione preliminare                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-det-edt-cod-fis      .
           move      spaces               to   w-det-edt-cod-flg      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Deviazione se Italiano o Estero             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        srt-naz-arc          not  = "IT "
                     go to emi-fil-xml-idf-150.
       emi-fil-xml-idf-110.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Italiano                                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Eccezione bolle doganali                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        srt-tip-iva          =    "6" and
                     srt-cod-bdg          =    zero
                     move  "99999999999"  to   w-det-edt-cod-fis
                     go to emi-fil-xml-idf-300.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test se presente Partita Iva            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        srt-prt-iva          =    zero
                     go to emi-fil-xml-idf-130.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Controllo formale partita IVA           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      srt-prt-iva          to   w-cnt-piv-piv          .
           perform   cnt-prt-iva-000      thru cnt-prt-iva-999        .
           if        w-cnt-piv-flg        =    spaces
                     go to emi-fil-xml-idf-120.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Segnale di errore in partita IVA        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rot-l02-tip-arc    to   w-err-ana-cof-tip      .
