      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Emissione tag 'EsigibilitaIVA'                  *
      *              *                                                 *
      *              * N.B.: solo Split Payment                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
