      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        srt-flg-rfp          not  = "S"
                     go to emi-fil-xml-rie-780.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Emissione                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "EsigibilitaIVA"     to   w-sta-emi-xml-pmt      .
           move      "E"                  to   w-sta-emi-xml-ope      .
           move      "S"                  to   w-sta-emi-xml-val      .
           move      "="                  to   w-sta-emi-xml-ind      .
           perform   emi-tag-xml-000      thru emi-tag-xml-999        .
       emi-fil-xml-rie-780.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
