      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Emissione file sequenziale in formato XML                 *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Riepilogo - castelletto Iva - Aliquota                    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       emi-fil-xml-ali-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Editing codice Iva                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      srt-cod-iva
                    (w-det-cst-iva-ctr)   to   w-edt-iva-cod          .
           perform   edt-cod-iva-000      thru edt-cod-iva-999        .
       emi-fil-xml-ali-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se aliquote di esenzione: ad emissione aliquota *
      *              * a zero                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-edt-iva-spc        =    3 or
                     w-edt-iva-spc        =    4 or
                     w-edt-iva-spc        =    5 or
                     w-edt-iva-spc        =    6
                     go to emi-fil-xml-ali-700.
       emi-fil-xml-ali-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Per le aliquote non detraibili o per gli omaggi *
      *              * si scorpora l'aliquota reale                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-edt-iva-spc        not  = 7 and
                     w-edt-iva-spc        not  = 9
                     go to emi-fil-xml-ali-600.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scorporo dell'aliquota                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-edt-iva-spc        =    7
                     subtract 700         from w-edt-iva-cie
           else if   w-edt-iva-spc        =    9
                     subtract 900         from w-edt-iva-cie          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A trattamento aliquota imponibile           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     emi-fil-xml-ali-600.
       emi-fil-xml-ali-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Aliquota imponibile                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   p-car                  .
           move      02                   to   p-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   p-sgn                  .
           move      "<B"                 to   p-edm                  .
           move      w-edt-iva-cie        to   p-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * In campo di emissione                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      p-edt                to   w-all-str-alf          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A emissione                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     emi-fil-xml-ali-800.
       emi-fil-xml-ali-700.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Aliquota a zero                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
