      *              * Test su contatore errori riscontrati            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-err-ana-cof-ctr    >    zero
                     go to emi-fil-xml-erm-050.
       emi-fil-xml-erm-020.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
