      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-sta-emi-csv-ctr    to   kk2-ctr-prg            .
           move      w-rot-l02-tip-arc    to   kk2-tip-rec            .
           move      srt-rec              to   kk2-srt-rec            .
