      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      srt-naz-arc          to   w-out-doc-naz-arc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice fiscale                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      srt-cod-fis          to   w-out-doc-cod-fis      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Partita IVA                             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   p-ope                  .
